Section 3 — The Artist Behind The Canvas

Split-screen layout.

Left:
Large portrait of Megan.

Right:

Meet Megan

Born in Detroit.

Inspired by movement.

Shaped by music.

Driven by storytelling.

Every piece begins long before paint touches canvas.

A short story ending with:

Read My Story →

Section 4 — Featured Collection

Not a product grid.

A gallery.

Large immersive images.

Each artwork gets breathing room.

Example:

