48" x 60"

Mixed Media

$4,750

"A reflection on memory and movement."

[View Artwork]

Section 5 — The Process

This is where collectors connect emotionally.

From Inspiration To Canvas
Inspiration
Sketch
Creation
Final Piece

Include studio photos.

Section 6 — Video Section

Large embedded reel.

Watch The Journey

See how music, movement, and visual art come together.

Visitors stay longer.

Trust increases.

Conversions improve.

Section 7 — Commission Experience

Dark background.

Premium feel.

Create Something Personal

Whether it's a private collection, statement piece, or meaningful gift, every commission is crafted around your story.

Button:

Start Your Commission

Section 8 — Testimonials

Collectors.

Gallery owners.

Art buyers.

Event organizers.

People trust people.

Section 9 — Latest Works

Carousel.

Not crowded.

3-5 pieces maximum.

Give artwork room to breathe.

Section 10 — Join The Inner Circle

Instead of:

❌ "Get 25% Off"

Use:

