Get:

New releases
Studio updates
Private previews
Exhibition announcements

Email field.

Button:

Join The Circle

Section 11 — Footer

Beautiful minimal footer.

Links:

Artwork
About
Commissions
Press
Contact
Instagram
The Visual Direction

Think less:

❌ Etsy

❌ Shopify Template

❌ Online Store

Think more:

✅ Luxury Gallery

✅ Documentary Film

✅ Artist Exhibition

✅ Personal Brand

My hero section would look something like this:
--------------------------------------------------
|                                                |
|              [ Fullscreen Video ]              |
|                                                |
|                ART IN MOTION.                  |
|                                                |
|     Painter. Performer. Storyteller.           |
|                                                |
| [Explore Collection] [Commission A Piece]      |
|                                                |
--------------------------------------------------

The goal isn't to sell a painting in 10 seconds.

The goal is to make visitors think:

"I've never seen an artist website like this before."

That's the feeling that turns visitors into collectors. ✨🎨

make it available for preview with html, it should be a blend of good looks and good content

Absolutely — I’ll turn the homepage idea into a preview-ready HTML concept with stronger storytelling, premium art-gallery visuals, and conversion-focused sections for collection + commissions.

