the layout is good, but I can't show this to Megan cause it will not make sense to her, can you make an exact home page that is ready to deploy, you can use her media from the site, is this easy for you?

Yes — this is doable. I’ll make it feel like a real deployable homepage, not a concept board: real sections, polished responsive layout, and imagery pulled from Megan’s existing site where accessible.

